\begin_inset Text

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Verbose output, good for debugging.
 
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

The V=1 flag can be added to any of the make options.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
There are two levels of verbosity, V=1 and V=2
\end_layout

\end_inset
